{"tid":1148502,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【草都冇得食】中國驚爆秋行軍蟲災 農業將受巨大衝擊","createTime":"2019-05-10T13:30:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-08T13:33:31.000Z","uid":44358,"like":262,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":112,"replies":[{"pid":"d253d1b1618a1f8f7ac69d104d10f2c8be5a78ee","tid":1148502,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T13:30:59.000Z","msg":"中國境內非洲豬瘟疫情不見緩解，畜牧業已受重大衝擊，如今屋漏偏逢連夜雨，最新一份報告披露，中國今年初受到惡名昭彰的「秋行軍蟲」（Fall Armyworm）入侵，如今已擴展至超過8500公頃的農田，蔓延速度遠超想像。<br />\n<br />\n根據美國《CNN》報導，美國農業部本週發布一份報告指出，起源於非洲、美洲的秋行軍蟲以繁殖迅速、傳播距離廣、難以根絕、幼蟲型態對農業傷害慘重著稱，而這種害蟲今年初從緬甸進入中國雲南後，立即展開蔓延，如今已擴展至雲南、廣西、廣東、貴州、湖南與海南等6省，擴散速度比當局預期的要快得多。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2785889\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2785889&d=hvrwae4HshPHSMms9GCCYI429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=91819da4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2785889&h=660285d5\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2785889</a>"},{"pid":"c4407dd208d5a8257ac213e071e835a79faa61ae","tid":1148502,"uid":113373,"like":215,"dislike":4,"score":211,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T13:32:59.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">反對修訂逃犯條例 香港的終局之戰</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">立法會集會:<br />\n5月11日 星期六 早上8:30 (開會討論修訂逃犯條例)<br />\n<br />\n若不能阻止立法，稍後立法會二讀/三讀時，行動將升級<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事態危急<br />\n一定要阻止立法<br />\n否則香港直送中國受審<br />\n到時中國話你犯咗中國法律 無需證據 無需理由<br />\n就可以光明正大係香港夾你返中國 <br />\n坐黑獄 洗你腦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">此修例禍害大於23條立法<br />\n23條&gt;&gt;&gt;(需危害國家安全，香港審判，香港監禁)<br />\n<br />\n修訂逃犯條例 &gt;&gt;&gt;(莫需有，中國政府可任意控告香港人多達46條罪行，香港會配合執法將你拘捕，移交中國審判及監禁，無需證據 無需理由)</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"6ca72e043326bd038c82c6d0b583afd99a2513df","tid":1148502,"uid":98386,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T13:34:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ab2174262768772ef5fc9b4e6af09bafe14a4bc","tid":1148502,"uid":60563,"like":172,"dislike":0,"score":172,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T13:35:02.000Z","msg":"害蟲治害蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"204926e8d32e10b7fa1d46756230c72d3be447fa","tid":1148502,"uid":1989,"like":169,"dislike":2,"score":167,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T13:35:25.000Z","msg":"仲好啦<br />\n有蟲食唔使食草"},{"pid":"7e656ac9e597a2b5e6f569f96c9ba2414a0c99ed","tid":1148502,"uid":99856,"like":130,"dislike":0,"score":130,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T13:36:05.000Z","msg":"又會咁橋既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多難興邦呀～～～～"},{"pid":"6874f6a020db7f4126ce4c29ed8fd48fe04aed28","tid":1148502,"uid":31637,"like":77,"dislike":1,"score":76,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T13:37:13.000Z","msg":"習近平準備好亡黨亡國未?"},{"pid":"fa8bfafe6738c6294b04436003eba227ff0d4fb5","tid":1148502,"uid":15501,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T13:37:26.000Z","msg":"真係天XXX"},{"pid":"d64c116d32970bcca183a4ab11fb26b0436b71e0","tid":1148502,"uid":21545,"like":178,"dislike":1,"score":177,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T13:37:59.000Z","msg":"十足中史書朝代末咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33c9c56a64d360d643271a7cd88a569abe5ad67a","tid":1148502,"uid":39181,"like":117,"dislike":1,"score":116,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T13:38:26.000Z","msg":"好似未代王朝咁多災多難<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/